en1KG<-read.table(my.dir %&% 'DGN-WB_exp_10-foldCV_elasticNet_alpha0.5_1000G_chr1-22_2015-04-02.txt',header=T)

lassoHap<-lassoHap[complete.cases(lassoHap),]
